{"tid":1104492,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(劇透)其實how I met your mother個ending都唔係好爛","createTime":"2019-04-13T07:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T07:43:25.000Z","uid":95520,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb92426f8a178173cfbd4831f05a59bf9dab3fb","tid":1104492,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T07:39:53.000Z","msg":"突然心血來潮重睇返last season<br />\n其實諗返,去到S7開始都好寫實<br />\n朋友愈來愈疏遠<br />\n幾個朋友喺酒吧聚埋一齊嘅時間同機會愈來愈少<br />\n反而我覺得最後個ending最符合現實<br />\n<br />\nBarney同Robin真係好襯,亦好有化學作用<br />\n但佢哋兩個都唔係識處理relationship嘅人<br />\n<br />\n甚至The mother死我都覺得唔大問題<br />\n<br />\nBarney人生雖然無愛情,但佢個女都徹底改變咗佢<br />\n呢點我幾鐘意,起碼佢唔使孤獨終老<br />\n<br />\n真係唯一最最最最大敗筆,一定係ted同robin又一齊返<br />\n前面咁多季已經證明咗ted同robin根本唔work<br />\n亦從來唔覺佢哋真係好夾"},{"pid":"6eada7ae25b28fa4e25adad2c26025b85a2b0d5d","tid":1104492,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"我都幾中意佢地嘅ending<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9962d0b9928252eb96ab7066a9887f19538f2f","tid":1104492,"uid":212331,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:00:35.000Z","msg":"Ted 同robin係廿幾歲時唔work<br />\n都唔代表四十幾歲時唔work既<br />\n不過都係果句<br />\n始終皆藍號<br />\n何故添黃傘"},{"pid":"ad56b80e7f3a70af4b0a6e86a813b26fef4b94a9","tid":1104492,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eada7ae25b28fa4e25adad2c26025b85a2b0d5d","tid":1104492,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"我都幾中意佢地嘅ending<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:42:55.000Z","msg":"反而個alternative ending好不知所謂"},{"pid":"67c13c2123b91537b373629e012b1033b6a86752","tid":1104492,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d9962d0b9928252eb96ab7066a9887f19538f2f","tid":1104492,"uid":212331,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:00:35.000Z","msg":"T